#<AdxTL>@(#)0.0.0.0 $Revision$ 
$ACTION
Case ACTION
   When "OUVRE"       : Gosub OUVRE
   When "DEBUT"       : Gosub DEBUT
Endcase

Return

$OUVRE

Gosub OUVRE_OUT From ESSEMPAV
#Manage Localisations
Call MANAGE_LOCALISATION("ESSEMPV") From DIVPAYE
Return

$DEBUT
Gosub DEBUT_OUT From ESSEMPAV
#Manage localisations
Call HIDE_ACTIVITYFIELDS From WESSEMPVHIDE
Call SHOW_LEGACTCALLS From WESSEMPVSHOW
Affzo [M:ESEMP]1-99
Return

